# Snapshot tests compare generated output byte-for-byte against checked-in
# fixtures, so working-tree text must stay LF on every platform (Windows
# runners default to core.autocrlf=true and would check out CRLF).
* text=auto eol=lf
*.dar binary
*.binpb binary
*.png binary
*.bundle binary
*.cmd text eol=crlf
*.bat text eol=crlf
